ons and invites us to experience the beauty of this elusive world.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 0aGhosts in art. 0aLandscape photographyzTexaszCaddo Lake National Wildlife Refuge. 0aWetland animalszTexas, EastvPictorial works. 0aWetlandszTexas, EastvPictorial works. 7aPhotography / General.2bisacsh  aArt, Photography, Ecology, Landscape, Surreal, Transcendent, Mysterious.1 aCarter, Keith, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJohnson, Bret Anthony, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts 2023z9783111318103oZDB-23-DPK08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2023 Englishz978311131903208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishz978311131929208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Texas Press Complete eBook-Package 2022z978311076651640uhttps://doi.org/10.7560/32655840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781477326565423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781477326565/original  a978-3-11-076651-6  University of Texas Press Complete eBook-Package 2022b2022  a978-3-11-131903-2  EBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2023 Englishb2023  a978-3-11-131929-2  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishb2023  aEBA_EMB  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2023  aZDB-23-DPKb2023